          "severity": "INR >8.0 (severe elevation)",
          "criteria": "major bleeding risk",
          "treatment": "Hold warfarin. Oral Vitamin K 2.5-5 mg (IV if major bleeding). IV Vitamin K 10 mg + FFP/PCC if life-threatening bleeding."
